sources.description:
He Fell In Love With The Nanny | A Nanny for Christmas | Hallmark Romance Movie - During the holiday season, a sharp young career woman takes a job as a nanny, bringing her into the lives of a busy Beverly Hills advertising executive and a no-nonsense company owner. As Christmas approaches, their worlds collide in unexpected ways, sparking laughter, heartfelt moments, and life-changing connections. Amid festive chaos, love, and personal growth, the holiday proves to be a turning point for all, reshaping their futures in ways they never imagined.

2010.  Stars: Emmanuelle Vaugier, Dean Cain, Richard Ruccolo
